REQUIRES Driver

D statheat  stationary heating
D qheat     intensity of the transient heating
D x0heat    X location of the transient heating
D y0heat    Y location of the transient heating
D z0heat    Z location of the transient heating
D sigheat   sigma of the transient heating
D tstar     start time of the transient
D t0heat    switch off time of the transient
D tau       decay time of the transient
D theatmin  Min heating temperature

PARAMETER statheat      REAL      1.0E-5  
PARAMETER qheat         REAL      0.0E0   
PARAMETER x0heat        REAL      1.0E0   
PARAMETER y0heat        REAL      1.0E0   
PARAMETER z0heat        REAL      1.0E0   
PARAMETER sigheat       REAL      1.0E0   
PARAMETER tstar         REAL     -1.0E0   
PARAMETER t0heat        REAL     -1.0E0   
PARAMETER tau           REAL      1.0E0   
PARAMETER theatmin      REAL      1.0E3   
PARAMETER useHeat   BOOLEAN TRUE 

VARIABLE enuc                # nuclear energy gen. rate
